  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/937860/extras/c2ddbafe67d7ea0daaed9439bb9b67b0.avif?t=1745520677\" width=630 height=126 /></span><br><strong>Are you ready for the craziest PvP battle  ever?</strong><br><br>Bigger guns is a competitive online PVP shooter game with IO and Deathmatch rules.<br>From giant lollipops to viking axes, everything is a weapon.<br>Choose your combat gear wisely and show everyone who is the best in the arena.<br>Pick up cash to level up and get stronger and faster.<br>Customize your warrior and battle in style with players from all over the world.<br>Build Maps to be played Online in DeathMatch, Battle Royale or just to hangout with your friends in Open Sandbox.<br>And, if you get bored...just <i>make it rain</i>.<br><br>• Fast-paced gameplay<br>• Cross-platform online battles<br>• Crazy character combinations <br>• Beautiful  Voxel Artwork with amazing color and effects<br>• Dynamic battles with lots of weapons (shotguns and chickens included)<br>• Integrated Workshop Map Builder<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/937860/extras/monk.png?t=1537266080?t=1745520677\" /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/937860/extras/c2ddbafe67d7ea0daaed9439bb9b67b0.avif?t=1745520677\" width=630 height=126 /></span><br><strong>Are you ready for the craziest PvP battle  ever?</strong><br><br>Bigger guns is a competitive online PVP shooter game with IO and Deathmatch rules.<br>From giant lollipops to viking axes, everything is a weapon.<br>Choose your combat gear wisely and show everyone who is the best in the arena.<br>Pick up cash to level up and get stronger and faster.<br>Customize your warrior and battle in style with players from all over the world.<br>Build Maps to be played Online in DeathMatch, Battle Royale or just to hangout with your friends in Open Sandbox.<br>And, if you get bored...just <i>make it rain</i>.<br><br>• Fast-paced gameplay<br>• Cross-platform online battles<br>• Crazy character combinations <br>• Beautiful  Voxel Artwork with amazing color and effects<br>• Dynamic battles with lots of weapons (shotguns and chickens included)<br>• Integrated Workshop Map Builder<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/937860/extras/monk.png?t=1537266080?t=1745520677\" /></span>",
